OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FShort prison sentence      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'derailed' woman's life    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The impact of short prison sentences on
OL,6, women and their families is a central  
OL,7, theme of the latest BBC One prison     
OL,8, drama Time. One woman - jailed for     
OL,9, stealing in her early 30s - says the   
OL,10, four months she spent behind bars      
OL,11, "totally derailed" her life.           
OL,13,F"I often think about how life might    
OL,14,Fhave been different without going to   
OL,15,Fprison," says Martha, who is using a   
OL,16,Fpseudonym.                             
OL,18,F"I don't think purely punishing someone
OL,19,Fand re-traumatising them helps them to 
OL,20,Fmove on with their lives."             
